        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2020-03-01 01:05:07.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Hmm - do we have actors with duplicate name? APPC and APPCLCM were\n > declared different right?\n\nCurrently, they're both \"APPC\" - I didn't change that.  AFAIK, the latter is no longer used, so it gets ignored.  Nothing has been done to upgrade APPC-LCM.  However, if we want to support both, we can certainly name them differently.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
